| Orphan-sweep Stop hook | **Flag-gated, default-off.** `SPECKIT_STOP_HOOK_ORPHAN_SWEEP=off` by default; `dry-run` logs only; `1`/`on`/`live` reaps. Cites: `021.../implementation-summary.md:55`, `021.../implementation-summary.md:108-110`, current `ENV_REFERENCE.md:178`. |
