| Dead-socket reap hardening | **Default-on with tunable retry.** `SPECKIT_LEASE_PROBE_RETRIES=1`, retry timeout `1500`, retry backoff `250`; `0` disables retry and restores single-probe behavior. Cites: `019.../implementation-summary.md:55`, current `ENV_REFERENCE.md:175-177`, current `.opencode/bin/lib/launcher-ipc-bridge.cjs:48-54`. |

